    N1["Trigger notes:\n1) API route triggers run_runtime_agent for every synchronous run.\n2) _start_agent_span is the tracing gateway and no-ops when disabled.\n3) graph_agent.run trigger is the execution boundary where failures can occur before success metadata exists."]
